name: Bojana Resto
address: 7GQP+M3H, Klumpu, Nusa Penida, Klungkung Regency, Bali 80771, Indonesia
review 1: They do not have all ingredients for meal. Breakfast are super poor. Prices are high + service fee and government taxes. Do not recommend this restaurant.
review 2: Nice atmosphere, delicious food with good products !  Service very good! (also offer vegetarian alternatives on request) Dinner starts from 6 p.m:)
